message.text:
What unforgettable moments at TamHunt 2025! 🌟

Our JPMAP-FEU students explored, bonded, and conquered challenges together — proof that learning can be exciting outside the classroom too. 

Thank you to everyone who joined and showed what teamwork and people management are all about. 

📸: Alec Fernan
💻: Jziann Pascua

#JPMAPFEUChapter
#JPMAPFEU_13

message.text:
What unforgettable moments at TamHunt 2025! 🌟

Our JPMAP-FEU students explored, bonded, and conquered challenges together — proof that learning can be exciting outside the classroom too. 

Thank you to everyone who joined and showed what teamwork and people management are all about. 

📸: Alec Fernan
💻: Jziann Pascua

#JPMAPFEUChapter
#JPMAPFEU_13
#JPMAPapaibigKaSaIloilo
